







@(A.1 = 1-9) My own mother gave birth to me for your sake, my @wDN{Ningal} gave birth to me for your sake. ……, my beloved heart will come. ……, my beloved heart will come there. May …… come to me (?), and I will rejoice over him. May @wDN{Dumuzid} come to me (?), and I will rejoice over him.
